OL,3,CTeenager missing after getting into
OL,4,Cdifficulty in water in Darley Abbey
OL,6,FA teenager is missing after getting
OL,7,Finto difficulty in water in Derby.
OL,9,FEmergency services were called to
OL,10,FDarley Abbey at around 12:46pm on
OL,11,FFriday (June 10th).
OL,13,FThey were responding to reports that a
OL,14,Fman, who is in his late teens, was
OL,15,Fswimming with another, younger
OL,16,Fteenager when the pair got into
OL,17,Fdifficulty just below the weir close
OL,18,Fto the Darley Abbey Mills complex.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
