OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1783777691
OL,3,CTeenager missing after getting into
OL,4,Cdifficulty in water in Darley Abbey
OL,6,FThe younger teenager was safely
OL,7,Fremoved from the water, and a search
OL,8,Fwas launched, involving both
OL,9,FDerbyshire Fire and Rescue Service and
OL,10,Fthe East Midlands Ambulance Service.
OL,12,FColleagues from both of those
OL,13,Forganisations have now left the scene,
OL,14,Fand specialist trained police divers
OL,15,Fare en route to continue the search.
OL,17,FDerbyshire Constabulary says the
OL,18,Fmissing man's family is aware of the
OL,19,Fsituation and is being kept up to date
OL,20,Fon the latest from the scene.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/3
